    "description": "All you need to do is kill the pills. Shoot your way to a new high score while collecting powerups to shake things up.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKill Pill is a simple arena shooter game where you shoot pills that randomly spawn around the map. There are six types of powerups you can get: speed (red), jump (blue), automatic firing (green), collateral damage (purple), shotgun (orange), and freezing time (white). Two modes are in the game. Classic mode only has red pills which run toward you. Arcade mode has 4 types of pills: red ones, orange ones which split in two when you shoot them, blue ones which jump with you, and green ones which are faster than you. Each kill is one point added to your score. High scores are saved between each session. How high can you go?",
